ðŸ§  Project Overview

The Smart Career & Internship Management System is a PHP + MySQL-based web application that connects students, recruiters, and companies through a unified career hub.  
It merges the professional networking features of LinkedIn with the matchmaking and recommendation style of Bumble, focusing exclusively on internships, student jobs, and career development.

The platform simplifies the internship and recruitment process by automating Resume analysis, skill-based job matching, and recruiter shortlisting â€” empowering both students and employers to connect efficiently.

ðŸš€ Key Features

