- Upload resumes (PDF/DOCX) and maintain multiple versions.  
- View and apply to internship/job postings based on eligibility and skills.  
- Track application status and recruiter feedback in real-time.  

ðŸ¢ Company & Recruiter Dashboard
- Post new Job/internship openings with detailed requirements (skills, CGPA, batch).  
- Manage recruiter accounts under a company.  
- View and search student resumes filtered by skills or academic performance.  
- Rate, review, and shortlist candidates directly.

ðŸ¤– Smart Matching & Analytics
- Intelligent skill-to-job mapping that automatically recommends top matches.  
- Resume parsing and metadata extraction for quick filtering.  
- Recruiter review analytics (rating averages, shortlist stats, feedback summaries).  

ðŸ” Authentication & Access Control
